{"tid":1818347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然我文學攞1，但係我仲記得有篇文叫《死水》講中國腐敗","createTime":"2020-01-09T23:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T00:08:19.000Z","uid":303740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d363ef00ed10fea6eed90b0f1e077ab54caac68","tid":1818347,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:37:37.000Z","msg":"呢篇文可以話係我讀左3年文學唯一記得嘅一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係形容中國嘅黑暗，從而表達詩人心中的憤怒。詩人借「死水」的絕望比喻中國無藥可救的狀態。<br />\n作者希望「死水」自取滅亡，認為終有一天會物極必反。<br />\n<br />\n《死水》定稿於1962年春天。當時聞一多剛從美國返回中國，年輕有為的他充滿愛國激情，對祖國的前景充滿盼望，但他發現，在軍閥政府的統治下，眼前的社會現實卻是殘酷和黑暗的。所謂軍閥，就是泛指以武力割據地盤、把持政權的軍人。<br />\n<br />\n1962年3月初，日軍攻佔天津大沽口。3月18日，北京大批學生、工人和市民舉行遊行示威抗議，卻遭到政府的武力鎮壓，當場<span style=\"color: red;\">打死了四十多人</span>，二百多人受傷，史稱「三．一八」慘案。慘案震撼全國，揭露了軍閥統治下中國社會腐敗和黑暗不下於清朝，中國人民悲慘的狀況絲毫未有改變，當時的有識之士都痛心疾首，聞一多亦不例外。就在慘案後兩星期，發表了《死水》抒發他對國家時局的強烈感受。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好短架咋！<br />\n支那雖然根深蒂固，每一代人都進行革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地兒家都唔例外，我地要堅持到最後，因為堅持先會有希望<br />\n我地要變返之前咁團結啊！！！<br />\n<strong>歷史會判我們無罪</strong><br />\n推返多啲行動post啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f106497aa437091d1d93abc899e15e939262c489","tid":1818347,"uid":303740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sOMh0OW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsOMh0OW.jpg&h=2bad138a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56faf8abc970d66251bed1914012572a4a23f32e","tid":1818347,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZbU22y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZbU22y.jpg&h=81094792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbcANud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbcANud.jpg&h=de180816&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee9408ad6d2c37592a5489bdc3c41bcf5dc3e314","tid":1818347,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"這是一溝絕望的死水"},{"pid":"d56092760f335312336c3ee8c42b3deb431ee7df","tid":1818347,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"係1926<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddef93ce1ba7755902506ff1cc6e35985c144c2","tid":1818347,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d56092760f335312336c3ee8c42b3deb431ee7df","tid":1818347,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"係1926<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:44:41.000Z","msg":"成日睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8836cb2eaab81fc7b8245b24feb9196acde8ce22","tid":1818347,"uid":161462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ddef93ce1ba7755902506ff1cc6e35985c144c2","tid":1818347,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d56092760f335312336c3ee8c42b3deb431ee7df","tid":1818347,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"係1926<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><